description:
In this new season of RuPaul’s Drag Race All Stars, there will be 18 queens - the largest in the franchise’s herstory - returning to compete in the ultimate competition for the crown. For the first time ever, a brand-new format will be introduced across 12 episodes: the Tournament of All Stars. The 18 queens returning to RuPaul’s Drag Race All Stars include: Acid Betty, Aja, Alyssa Hunter, Bosco, Cynthia Lee Fontaine, Daya Betty, DeJa Skye, Denali, Ginger Minj, Irene the Alien, Jorgeous, Kerri Colby, Lydia B. Kollins, Mistress Isabelle Brooks, Nicole Paige Brooks, Olivia Lux, Phoenix, and Tina Burner.

This season dives deep into the disturbed minds behind these crimes, uncovering shocking twists and relentless pursuits of justice.

Stream the new season of the hit P+ Original docuseries, FBI TRUE on May 20 on Paramount+.
